Menu - Class in presentation
This class creates the appropriate interface for a client when he wants to see the menu All products from the menu are showed into a JTable from where the client can choose the menuitem, by selecting a chechbox, to order Also, the client can search for a certain product by introducing keywords into the JTextfield present on the interface (the method searchProduct is called)
